## 🛠️ 2. Technology Stack
The project is built on a modern, high-performance React stack:
- **Framework**: [Next.js 15 (App Router)](https://nextjs.org/)
- **Language**: [TypeScript](https://www.typescriptlang.org/)
- **UI & Styling**: 
  - [Tailwind CSS v4](https://tailwindcss.com/)
  - [Shadcn UI](https://ui.shadcn.com/) & Radix UI Primitives (Accessible components)
  - [Framer Motion](https://www.framer.com/motion/) (Animations)
  - [Aceternity UI](https://ui.aceternity.com/) (e.g., [background-beams.tsx](file:///c:/Workspace/Portfolio-forge/src/components/ui/background-beams.tsx))
- **State Management**: [Zustand v5](https://zustand-demo.pmnd.rs/) (Client-side global state)
- **Data Fetching**: [TanStack React Query v5](https://tanstack.com/query) (Server state synchronization)
- **Authentication**: [Clerk](https://clerk.com/) (`@clerk/nextjs`)
- **Forms & Validation**: [React Hook Form](https://react-hook-form.com/) + [Zod](https://zod.dev/)
- **Icons**: [Lucide React](https://lucide.dev/)
- **Utilities**: `date-fns`, `luxon`, `clsx`, `tailwind-merge`

